785
01:01:42,943 --> 01:01:44,486
Just calm down!

786
01:01:44,570 --> 01:01:47,072
- I'm gonna live my own life!
- Stop!

787
01:02:04,089 --> 01:02:07,092
I know things are difficult.

788
01:02:07,176 --> 01:02:09,136
I know you wanna have fun.

789
01:02:09,178 --> 01:02:12,806
At that age girls wanna see boys and

790
01:02:12,890 --> 01:02:16,560
go somewhere dark and
smooch... when I was young I...

791
