But you gotta try
your best until the finals.

792
01:02:22,816 --> 01:02:25,361
You even brought your family here.

793
01:02:25,444 --> 01:02:27,363
Don't worry too much
about picking the song.

794
01:02:27,446 --> 01:02:30,074
It's your choice so you just...

795
01:02:30,157 --> 01:02:31,867
I didn't believe you when you said that

796
01:02:34,036 --> 01:02:36,580
I'll get hurt and end up alone.

797
01:02:38,249 --> 01:02:42,461
- You were listening?
- I still don't wanna admit it.

798
01:02:43,837 --> 01:02:46,173
Life's been too hard for that.

799
01:02:50,469 --> 01:02:52,179
Can I ask you something?

800
01:02:56,684 --> 01:02:58,394
I don't remember my mom.

801
01:03:01,272 --> 01:03:02,898
<i>Cuz</i> I hate her.

802
01:03:06,193 --> 01:03:10,406
I have no memory of her
but hatred. Am I bad?

803
01:03:16,120 --> 01:03:17,746
I want to forgive her.

804
01:03:20,624 --> 01:03:23,460
But she brought all of us together

805
01:03:24,211 --> 01:03:27,339
lived her own life and died her own way.

806
01:03:31,135 --> 01:03:34,555
I've never blamed the kids
no matter how hard it got.

807
01:03:39,935 --> 01:03:45,274
She caused so much pain

808
01:03:46,567 --> 01:03:48,068
And suffering in my life.

809
01:03:50,571 --> 01:03:53,991
Now I can't even be angry at her.

810
01:03:54,074 --> 01:03:55,492
I can never forgive her for that.

811
01:03:58,746 --> 01:04:00,289
Am I bad?

812
01:04:21,518 --> 01:04:24,730
So, do you wanna live anywhere over here?

813
01:04:25,439 --> 01:04:28,942
Do you see that star that's blinking?

814
01:04:29,026 --> 01:04:29,943
Yeah.

815
01:04:30,027 --> 01:04:32,446
Do you think that's a shooting star?

816
01:04:34,448 --> 01:04:37,159
Rosie, what do you think about
living in one of these places?

817
01:04:37,242 --> 01:04:39,453
I think that one's Cinderella's castle.

818
01:04:39,536 --> 01:04:41,580
Cinderella's castle?

819
01:04:42,831 --> 01:04:44,166
That's nice.

820
01:05:05,270 --> 01:05:07,981
Why don't you wanna go to orphanage?

821
