843
01:07:30,499 --> 01:07:34,628
<i>I don't know if it worked</i>
<i>or not. But, anyway.</i>

844
01:07:34,711 --> 01:07:37,256
If <i>you're watching this,</i>

845
01:07:37,297 --> 01:07:40,634
<i>it would mean that I haven't</i>
<i>kept my promise again...</i>

846
01:07:40,717 --> 01:07:43,929
<i>Oh, I'm really really sorry.</i>

847
01:07:44,429 --> 01:07:46,139
<i>But, listen, kids.</i>

848
01:07:46,223 --> 01:07:50,644
Will you be sure to cut June's
birthday cake together for me?

849
01:07:51,937 --> 01:07:54,856
<i>Throw a great</i> party
<i>for her! Okay?</i>

850
01:07:54,940 --> 01:07:59,653
<i>Oh, I have presents for all of you as well.</i>

851
01:07:59,736 --> 01:08:02,948
<i>They are 'thanks-for-</i><i>
<i>going-to-church'presents!</i>

852
01:08:05,659 --> 01:08:08,078
<i>Hey! What are you waiting for?</i>

853
01:08:08,161 --> 01:08:09,371
Go <i>find them, quick!</i>

854
01:08:09,454 --> 01:08:10,455
Found it!

855
01:08:10,539 --> 01:08:13,166
<i>Hurry up! Quick!</i>
Go <i>find em.</i>

856
01:08:13,250 --> 01:08:14,418
<i>Quick, quick, quick!</i>

857
01:08:18,088 --> 01:08:22,134
I think your mom wanted to do this at home

858
01:08:22,175 --> 01:08:24,011
but I brought it here.

859
01:08:27,806 --> 01:08:29,433
<i>June, you there?</i>

860
01:08:30,892 --> 01:08:34,146
<i>I got some money.</i>

861
01:08:34,187 --> 01:08:39,151
<i>I prepared a little</i>
<i>something for your</i> party.

862
01:08:39,192 --> 01:08:41,153
<i>You must be mad at me again</i>

863
01:08:43,196 --> 01:08:46,533
<i>For wasting money, you'd say.</i>

864
01:08:48,535 --> 01:08:49,745
Oh, it fits!

865
01:08:52,706 --> 01:08:58,545
<i>I wanted to apologize</i>

866
01:08:59,546 --> 01:09:04,968
<i>You were right about what</i>
<i>you said last time we fought.</i>

867
01:09:06,053 --> 01:09:10,557
<i>That I'm chasing dreams and</i>

868
01:09:10,641 --> 01:09:15,395
<i>making your lives miserable.</i>

869
01:09:16,688 --> 01:09:21,109
<i>But June, youguys are always in my songs.</i>

870
01:09:21,985 --> 01:09:24,196
<i>I sing for you guys.</i>

871
01:09:24,279 --> 01:09:30,118
<i>And singing for you makes me happy.</i>

872
01:09:31,495 --> 01:09:35,415
So <i>I'm always thankful for you.</i>

873
01:09:35,499 --> 01:09:38,627
<i>And I'm sorry</i> too.

874
01:09:40,796 --> 01:09:43,840
<i>My sweet baby June.</i>

875
01:09:43,924 --> 01:09:46,134
<i>Things aren't easy, right?</i>

876
01:09:50,514 --> 01:09:56,144
<i>I'll try harder.</i>
<i>Try my best.</i>

877
01:09:56,228 --> 01:10:03,228
<i>I'll work hard so that</i>
<i>my baby June can be happy.</i>

878
01:10:06,822 --> 01:10:09,658
<i>I love you, June.</i>
<i>Happy Birthday!</i>

879
01:10:20,627 --> 01:10:22,379
This is for June!

880
01:10:24,756 --> 01:10:27,175
June! This is for you!

881
01:10:37,853 --> 01:10:41,690
June, are you crying?

882
01:10:56,079 --> 01:10:57,497
Mom!

883
01:10:58,790 --> 01:11:00,500
Mom!

884
01:11:33,450 --> 01:11:35,786
Happy birthday to you, June!

885
01:11:35,869 --> 01:11:38,705
You're looking nice today, June!

886
01:11:38,747 --> 01:11:41,500
You look young
for your age. June!

887
01:11:41,541 --> 01:11:43,376
Thanks for everything, June!

888
01:11:43,460 --> 01:11:46,171
Happy birthday to ya!
June!

889
01:11:55,055 --> 01:11:57,390
You making a cocktail?
Throw that out!

890
01:12:13,698 --> 01:12:14,950
Throw it!

891
01:12:17,536 --> 01:12:19,037
- Run away!
- Run!

892
01:12:19,120 --> 01:12:26,120
Window... a... magical goose
came and... landed in her...

893
01:12:31,049 --> 01:12:35,262
- A beautiful princess.
- A beautiful princess!

894
01:12:38,431 --> 01:12:39,891
Fighting!

895
01:12:49,192 --> 01:12:50,443
<i>EXCLUSIVE CONTRACT</i>

896
01:12:50,569 --> 01:12:53,196
Things are on a roll here!

897
01:12:54,364 --> 01:12:56,783
Great soup!

898
01:12:57,951 --> 01:12:59,202
Stamp it!

899
01:12:59,286 --> 01:13:01,705
This is too quick.

900
01:13:01,788 --> 01:13:03,498
I'm in a hurry!

901
01:13:03,582 --> 01:13:06,001
My girl band is releasing
a single next month.

902
01:13:06,084 --> 01:13:10,922
I have to get their choreography
and do all their PR!

903
01:13:10,964 --> 01:13:12,591
It's just that...

904
01:13:12,674 --> 01:13:15,343
I'll minus the <i>thirty</i> grand
you spent on Mila.

905
01:13:15,427 --> 01:13:17,429
I won't kill you and minus
<i>thirty</i> grand off your debt.

906
01:13:17,512 --> 01:13:20,140
You're good luck.

907
01:13:20,223 --> 01:13:23,435
You know my temper, right?
I would've killed you already.

908
01:13:23,518 --> 01:13:26,146
Thank you.
But...

909
01:13:27,022 --> 01:13:32,861
If June goes to Korea,
what'll happen to her family?

910
01:13:34,154 --> 01:13:36,865
They're not her family.
They're not blood-related!

911
01:13:36,948 --> 01:13:41,161
But she'll never wanna go
to Korea because of them.

912
01:13:42,037 --> 01:13:43,788
Damn it!

913
01:13:44,456 --> 01:13:46,791
Sir, I mean...

914
01:13:46,833 --> 01:13:49,669
Come on, Mr. Dough!

915
01:13:49,753 --> 01:13:52,380
We got this huge market in US.

916
01:13:52,464 --> 01:13:53,882
People kill to come here.

917
01:13:53,965 --> 01:13:56,801
Let's first win the audition

918
01:13:56,843 --> 01:13:57,886
and release an album.

919
01:13:57,969 --> 01:13:59,387
Then Korea's out of the question.

920
01:13:59,471 --> 01:14:02,474
You got <i>thirty</i> grand on you?

921
01:14:02,557 --> 01:14:04,601
Or you wanna rot in jail in Korea?

922
01:14:04,684 --> 01:14:08,980
I'm cutting you some slack
<i>cuz</i> you're their papa.

923
01:14:10,482 --> 01:14:11,816
Screw this!

924
01:14:11,858 --> 01:14:14,527
Rip up the contract and

925
01:14:14,611 --> 01:14:16,029
let's go back to Korea.

926
01:14:16,112 --> 01:14:18,740
I'll cut you up and see if you
got <i>thirty</i> grand in there.

927
01:14:23,119 --> 01:14:24,663
Look, you moron.

928
01:14:25,121 --> 01:14:30,251
Wake up, you idiot!
Smarten up!

929
01:14:33,838 --> 01:14:40,838
Then what will happen to her
family if she goes to Korea?

930
01:14:44,432 --> 01:14:49,062
Well, I don't know.

931
01:14:51,731 --> 01:14:55,193
I guess you'll have to help.

932
01:14:58,571 --> 01:15:00,991
Yeah?
Okay?

933
01:15:34,232 --> 01:15:35,942
- Nice job!
- Yeah!

934
01:15:36,026 --> 01:15:40,071
Yes! Nice job, big G!
Rosie!

935
01:15:42,115 --> 01:15:44,659
Think this is funny?

936
01:15:45,535 --> 01:15:47,579
Think I wanna joke around?

937
01:15:48,621 --> 01:15:51,958
Don't you immature brats know anything?

938
01:15:54,627 --> 01:15:55,962
Get the hell out.

939
01:15:58,631 --> 01:16:00,258
Get the hell out of here!

940
01:16:37,420 --> 01:16:39,339
Looking back,

941
01:16:40,715 --> 01:16:42,967
I think I liked you the most.

942
01:16:44,844 --> 01:16:47,972
We're similar.
Both selfish.

943
01:16:49,641 --> 01:16:51,142
In the end...

944
01:17:11,746 --> 01:17:14,624
Papa!
Papa!

945
01:17:24,092 --> 01:17:25,343
Papa!

946
01:17:37,021 --> 01:17:41,442
I never wake up before 11 am
so don't wake me up.

947
01:17:42,527 --> 01:17:46,447
You don't know what's behind
this friendly-looking face.

948
01:17:52,036 --> 01:17:55,874
I'll be going to Korea in a few days.

949
01:17:55,915 --> 01:17:58,459
What'll happen to the kids

950
01:17:58,543 --> 01:18:01,963
if you're giving up your guardianship?

951
01:18:04,257 --> 01:18:06,885
- Got more rice?
- Asshole.

952
01:18:11,431 --> 01:18:17,228
Gordon Jackson, Maya Hashim,
Jimmy Taylor...

953
01:18:17,270 --> 01:18:21,816
Tommy Taylor, and Rosie Valencia.

954
01:18:23,401 --> 01:18:27,530
The children will be sent to
the same facility for now.

955
01:18:28,114 --> 01:18:30,533
Afterwards, we'll go through
the procedure of finding

956
01:18:30,617 --> 01:18:33,536
the appropriate facility for each child.

957
01:18:33,620 --> 01:18:37,040
June, your custody status is still valid.

958
01:18:37,123 --> 01:18:39,542
However because you're a minor,

959
01:18:39,626 --> 01:18:42,045
if you can't contact the guardian,

960
01:18:42,128 --> 01:18:44,547
you'll need to request police protection.

961
01:18:44,631 --> 01:18:46,925
And I also need to be notified.

962
01:18:49,219 --> 01:18:51,054
Honey, in this country,

963
01:18:51,221 --> 01:18:55,558
