964
01:18:57,143 --> 01:19:01,189
- It's the very basis for...
- He'll call.

965
01:19:03,524 --> 01:19:05,652
There's still hope.

966
01:19:12,158 --> 01:19:13,952
Won't you listen to what I say?

967
01:19:14,035 --> 01:19:16,996
You guys, Rosie, please open the door!

968
01:19:17,080 --> 01:19:18,998
No! Go away!

969
01:19:19,082 --> 01:19:21,125
Please.
Sorry Rosie.

970
01:19:22,877 --> 01:19:24,837
You just need to be there
for a little while.

971
01:19:24,879 --> 01:19:27,715
Soon, I'll be there to get you, Rosie.

972
01:19:27,799 --> 01:19:31,511
Liars!
All adults are lying!

973
01:19:32,011 --> 01:19:34,806
June, you're also lying!

974
01:19:39,018 --> 01:19:43,648
Gordon, why are you also acting like this?

975
01:19:43,690 --> 01:19:45,817
Jimmy, Tommy, open up.

976
01:19:46,401 --> 01:19:48,361
I told Phoebe all about your dad,

977
01:19:48,403 --> 01:19:50,029
how he might be back for you.

978
01:19:50,113 --> 01:19:52,031
